680
00:50:43,870 --> 00:50:45,750
The two of you...

681
00:50:45,750 --> 00:50:47,470
A one-night stand?

682
00:50:47,470 --> 00:50:49,960
No, no! You've misunderstood!

683
00:50:51,120 --> 00:50:53,330
Teacher Wang, I know your math is very good,

684
00:50:53,330 --> 00:50:55,440
