688
00:51:02,530 --> 00:51:05,780
Take care of your own problems.

689
00:51:05,780 --> 00:51:07,220
You...

690
00:51:07,220 --> 00:51:09,980
Let the past stay in the past. Take hold of the present.

691
00:51:09,980 --> 00:51:13,490
Today's sit-in lecture was very successful.

692
00:51:13,490 --> 00:51:16,810
