694
00:51:20,550 --> 00:51:23,130
Boss, I haven't cleared things up yet. The two of us really aren't—

695
00:51:23,130 --> 00:51:25,470
Excuse me, I have other matters, so I'll take my leave.

696
00:51:25,470 --> 00:51:27,250
Teacher Wang!

697
00:51:31,150 --> 00:51:34,520
The new guy seems to have a great personality, huh?

698
00:51:35,400 --> 00:51:37,350
He seems skilled.

699
00:51:37,350 --> 00:51:40,590
People with true skills have this kind of temper.

700
00:51:40,590 --> 00:51:42,580
It's called pride.

701
00:51:44,130 --> 00:51:49,420
Right. He has this lofty aura, like a hero looking down at you.

702
00:51:49,420 --> 00:51:52,220
Proud and aloof, standing above the crowd.

703
00:51:52,220 --> 00:51:54,480
Just like a...

704
00:51:54,480 --> 00:51:56,510
A lion?

705
00:51:56,510 --> 00:51:59,260
A lion. Yes.

706
00:51:59,260 --> 00:52:00,760
The lion, Wang Qiangda.

707
00:52:00,760 --> 00:52:03,520
No, no. The lion king, Qiangda.

708
00:52:03,520 --> 00:52:06,460
Not bad! We can use that on the advertisements.

709
00:52:07,500 --> 00:52:10,650
I'm just a small, little plant here. I'll take my leave.

710
00:52:10,650 --> 00:52:12,970
Teacher Wang, we haven't discussed your salary yet.

711
00:52:12,970 --> 00:52:16,800
And we haven't discussed your sit-in lecture yet.

712
00:52:16,800 --> 00:52:20,010
But I really have another appointment. I only have an hour.

713
00:52:20,010 --> 00:52:21,770
One hour is enough.

714
00:52:21,770 --> 00:52:24,350
I don't treat often. Let's go eat.

715
00:52:24,350 --> 00:52:26,070
True, you never treat.

716
00:52:26,070 --> 00:52:28,540
- Yeah.
- It'll be a long time before it happens again.

717
00:52:28,540 --> 00:52:30,480
Teacher Guo, you clean up.

718
00:52:30,480 --> 00:52:32,510
We won't disturb you. Bye.

719
00:52:32,510 --> 00:52:34,400
Let's go.

720
00:52:35,740 --> 00:52:38,310
Here, here. Cheers!

721
00:52:38,310 --> 00:52:41,360
Xiao Wei.

722
00:52:41,360 --> 00:52:43,710
Cheers, boss.

723
00:52:47,520 --> 00:52:51,460
I'd like to ask if I've been accepted or not.

724
00:52:52,910 --> 00:52:54,520
Yes.

725
00:52:54,520 --> 00:52:57,520
Yes, there's a plan.

726
00:52:57,520 --> 00:53:01,630
The plan is, if you enroll in Wang Qiangda's Math Essentials course,

727
00:53:01,630 --> 00:53:05,120
you also get to take Wang Qiangwei's Comprehensive History course.

728
00:53:05,120 --> 00:53:05,860
It's a package?!

729
00:53:05,860 --> 00:53:09,830
Or you can have a Yo-kai watch.
(manga character)

730
00:53:09,830 --> 00:53:11,690
Yo-kai watch?

731
00:53:11,690 --> 00:53:14,000
Most of the students picked the watch.

732
00:53:14,000 --> 00:53:18,340
But don't be discouraged. Some students still picked your class.

733
00:53:19,390 --> 00:53:22,410
Right, right. So, what about my salary?

734
00:53:22,410 --> 00:53:25,500
Come on, don't ask that kind of question here.

735
00:53:25,500 --> 00:53:26,630
It's so awkward.

736
00:53:26,630 --> 00:53:31,090
Old Yan, she just got into the cram school business, so you should be more generous.

737
00:53:31,090 --> 00:53:32,550
Since when were you so considerate?

738
00:53:32,550 --> 00:53:34,790
You pay her salary then.

739
00:53:36,450 --> 00:53:39,130
All right, the rest of you, don't look.

740
00:53:41,420 --> 00:53:43,090
This much.

741
00:53:44,350 --> 00:53:46,110
<i>[2,600 TWD (86 USD)/Hour]</i>

742
