<i>[3,000 TWD (100 USD)/Hour]</i>

743
00:53:55,710 --> 00:53:57,240
This much.

744
00:53:57,240 --> 00:53:58,400
<i>[2,700 TWD (90 USD)/Hour]</i>

745
00:53:58,400 --> 00:54:01,340
That's my final offer. No more negotiating.

746
00:54:01,340 --> 00:54:04,120
But I can give you a proposal.

747
00:54:04,120 --> 00:54:09,130
For each additional student who enlists in your class, I'll add 500 TWD (16 USD) to your monthly salary.

748
00:54:09,130 --> 00:54:14,700
But first, you have to subtract the students who first enrolled in Wang Qiangda's math class.

749
00:54:14,700 --> 00:54:16,950
You can do the calculation, right?

750
00:54:17,820 --> 00:54:22,770
So, M is the total number of students.

751
00:54:22,770 --> 00:54:26,000
And N is that lion's students?!

752
00:54:26,000 --> 00:54:28,640
Hey, your math's not bad.

753
00:54:28,640 --> 00:54:31,070
I'm the one whose math isn't bad.

754
00:54:31,070 --> 00:54:32,800
Of course, your math's not bad.

755
00:54:32,800 --> 00:54:36,430
It's just not strong (qiangda) enough.

756
00:54:43,400 --> 00:54:47,960
Qiangwei, he's always like that in the beginning.

757
00:54:47,960 --> 00:54:51,830
As long as you're capable though, you don't have to worry about increasing your pay later.

758
00:54:53,520 --> 00:54:55,430
I'll work hard.

759
00:54:56,670 --> 00:54:58,820
Let me toast everyone.

760
00:54:58,820 --> 00:55:02,630
Please take care of me in the future.

761
00:55:02,630 --> 00:55:05,680
Good luck to you all.

