773
00:56:14,740 --> 00:56:17,260
Finish eating and head upstairs.

774
00:56:17,260 --> 00:56:18,780
Okay.

775
00:56:21,120 --> 00:56:24,120
Qiangda, please take care of Xiao Qing.

776
00:56:24,120 --> 00:56:27,770
I can only cook. I don't know about anything else.

777
00:56:27,770 --> 00:56:31,490
As long as she wants to learn, of course, I'm willing to teach her.

778
00:56:31,490 --> 00:56:34,690
But what's important is what she finds interesting.

779
00:56:34,690 --> 00:56:38,690
What do kids know about their interests? They just need to study.

780
00:56:44,590 --> 00:56:48,090
Eat slowly. If a girl saw you eating like that, she'd be scared off.

781
00:56:48,090 --> 00:56:51,380
He's a food goblin! And he met...

782
00:56:51,380 --> 00:56:53,320
- Uncle Xun!
- Hello.

783
00:56:53,320 --> 00:56:55,890
- I want the same. Chef's Special.
- Have a seat.

784
00:56:55,890 --> 00:56:57,270
Brother Xiao Tie!

785
00:56:57,270 --> 00:56:59,300
- Hey, there.
- What were you about to say?

786
00:56:59,300 --> 00:57:02,620
I was just about to say that this food goblin met the queen of darkness.

787
00:57:02,620 --> 00:57:05,300
- You've said too much.
- Queen of darkness?

788
00:57:05,300 --> 00:57:07,160
Is she part of a crime syndicate?

789
00:57:07,160 --> 00:57:09,570
Or Qiangda's girlfriend?

790
00:57:09,570 --> 00:57:12,930
Or a video game? Hurry and spill!

791
00:57:12,930 --> 00:57:15,020
Well...

792
00:57:15,690 --> 00:57:17,530
I'll cook you something delicious.

793
00:57:17,530 --> 00:57:19,970
Okay, then I'll tell you!

794
00:57:19,970 --> 00:57:24,950
My old classmate and current roommate is a bit eccentric, and he doesn't like crowds.

795
00:57:24,950 --> 00:57:26,910
But he does enjoy eating delicious food.

796
00:57:26,910 --> 00:57:29,670
There's a restaurant where you dine in the dark, and some of their food's pretty good.

797
00:57:29,670 --> 00:57:31,420
This food goblin went to try it out.

798
00:57:31,420 --> 00:57:36,770
But who knew that, while he was trying it out, he would meet this so-called queen of darkness.

799
00:57:41,070 --> 00:57:43,020
<i>That place is pitch black.</i>

800
00:57:43,020 --> 00:57:46,730
<i>You can't even see your fingers on an outstretched hand. Like you're blind.</i>

801
00:57:46,730 --> 00:57:50,630
<i>You have to leave any device that can emit light in the restaurant's care.</i>

802
00:57:50,630 --> 00:57:53,220
<i>The server will guide you to your table with a night-vision device.</i>

803
00:57:53,220 --> 00:57:56,190
<i>If you go to eat alone, there's a chance you'll end up sharing a table.</i>

804
00:57:56,190 --> 00:58:01,630
<i>You might not even know who's sitting right across from you.</i>

805
00:58:07,400 --> 00:58:11,240
<i>But maybe because you can't see each other, there's no pressure.</i>

806
00:58:11,240 --> 00:58:13,190
<i>You loosen up.</i>

807
00:58:14,020 --> 00:58:20,160
<i>And so, this food goblin very naturally ended up eating with a woman.</i>

808
00:58:21,700 --> 00:58:23,860
<i>In the end, he even got a bit drunk.</i>

809
00:58:23,860 --> 00:58:29,440
<i>In a woman's world, "If you love me, you should come find me."</i>

810
00:58:38,490 --> 00:58:41,270
So then what happened?

811
00:58:41,270 --> 00:58:45,460
All I know is that that night, this food goblin was both rational

812
00:58:45,460 --> 00:58:47,940
and yet sensitive and romantic.

813
00:58:47,940 --> 00:58:50,790
He had a very pleasant chat with his queen of darkness.

814
00:58:50,790 --> 00:58:53,870
They spoke from the bottom of their hearts and felt like they were floating in the air.

815
00:58:53,870 --> 00:58:55,400
In the end...

816
00:58:55,400 --> 00:58:57,640
What happened?

817
00:58:57,640 --> 00:59:02,160
