Qiangda, I still have to tell you that you shouldn't keep getting stuck inside it.

870
01:02:38,350 --> 01:02:42,470
Uncle Xun, this involves my dad's reputation and my mom's final wish before she died.

871
01:02:42,470 --> 01:02:46,600
