931
01:06:25,310 --> 01:06:29,080
There are a lot of options around Taipei.

932
01:06:29,080 --> 01:06:33,830
Jiannan Mountain and Elephant Mountain are both pretty nice.

933
01:06:33,830 --> 01:06:38,810
<i>Then shout into the distance, releasing everything you're holding inside.</i>

934
01:06:38,810 --> 01:06:41,230
<i>You'll feel a lot better.</i>

935
01:06:41,230 --> 01:06:44,210
<i>Maybe some people will find this a bit silly,</i>

936
01:06:44,210 --> 01:06:49,220
<i>but that's because you're really concerned about what others think of you.</i>

937
01:06:49,220 --> 01:06:52,080
<i>These are all invisible forces of stress.</i>

938
01:06:56,420 --> 01:06:58,440
<i>There's a certain beauty to accidents.</i>

939
01:06:58,440 --> 01:07:03,800
<i>Many beautiful things happen by chance.</i>

940
01:07:03,800 --> 01:07:08,070
<i>Let me ask you this. Did you choose your parents?</i>

941
01:07:08,070 --> 01:07:10,320
<i>You didn't, right?</i>

942
01:07:10,320 --> 01:07:16,490
<i>So your birth and life up to this day is the most beautiful chance happening.</i>

943
01:07:16,490 --> 01:07:18,140
<i>Why are you pulling it?</i>

944
01:07:18,140 --> 01:07:20,860
<i>Daddy!</i>

945
01:07:20,860 --> 01:07:24,080
<i>But the chance happenings that belong to me aren't beautiful.</i>

946
01:07:24,080 --> 01:07:26,720
<i>They're cruel and repulsive.</i>

947
01:07:27,870 --> 01:07:32,400
Wang Qiangda, as a man, you should take responsibility for your actions!

948
01:07:32,400 --> 01:07:34,730
